      },
      "date": "2015-01-16 23:13:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/8e8eed76-9dd2-11e4-858d-5254006e85c2).  Ran 20 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
