      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/6ef52d16-9ee7-11e4-91b3-5254006e85c2).  Ran 18 tests.  No failures.",
