        "subject": "LU-5937 llite: merge attr for striped dir in dir_ioctl",
        "message": "LU-5937 llite: merge attr for striped dir in dir_ioctl\n\nIn ll_dir_ioctl (LL_IOC_MDC_GETINFO), if the inode is\na striped directory, it should merge the attributes\nfrom all of stripes. So lfs find --size can get correct\nresult.\n\nRemove some unnecesary merging in ll_revalidate_slave(), and\nthe attributes will be stored in each stripe, only\nmerging them if required.\n\nChange-Id: I5b3b261d2798ab06226b28958a46e5c670e7e42a\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@intel.com>\n"
      },
